COMMON.cpp

  hr - draws a horizontal line
  input - gets a line of text from stdin
  cint - gets an integer from an std::string
  pause - waits for enter
  clearscreen - cls on windows clear on linux
  getmappedindex -
    returns an integer that has been mapped to a string
    returns negative one on failure to find the string in the map
  mapintoncamap - maps an integer to a string
  center - prints the given text centered horizontally
  present - typewriter text printing effect
  dialogue - uses clearscreen, present, and pause to create a character speaking dialogue

  DrawBoxTop - outputs the top of a UI box
  DrawBoxBottom - outputs the bottom of a UI box
  random - returns a psuedorandom integer between given min and max range

CTIMER.cpp

  CTIMER class - basic timer with ms resolution

KEYDRIVER.cpp

  KEYDRIVER class - implements poor kbhit() and getch() based keyboard input handling

STRINGUTILITY.cpp

  STRINGUTILITY class - string replace utility class

ABILITY.cpp

  ABILITY class - character abilities

BATTLE.cpp

  BATTLE class - the battle system

ITEM.cpp

  ITEM class - represents items in the game

HACK_TheTriggers.cpp

  all the triggers in the game

HACK_TheItems.cpp

  all the items in the game

HACK_TheAbilities.cpp

  all the abilities in the game

HACK_TheWORLDMAPCode.cpp

  the worldmap

HACK_TheENTITYCode.cpp

  the entity class implementation

HACK_TheGameCode.cpp

  the whole game

ingameMenuSystem.cpp

  all the menus



-D NODEBUG_BUILD  
-D NOMAP_TESTER  
-D NOALLOW_DEBUG_PAUSE 
-D NOSHOW_RANDOM_VALUES_BEFORE_RETURN


------------------------------------------------------------
MAIN GAME LOOP
------------------------------------------------------------

while playing:
  check for events
  if story progress end game flag is set:
    set playing to false
  if player is dead
    set playing to false
    show game over screen
  else
    clear screen
    render mini map
    init key driver
    get key press
    if esc key    set playing to false
    if up key     navigate hero north
    if down key   navigate hero south
    if left key   navigate hero west
    if right key  navigate hero east
    if tab key    handle action commands

------------------------------------------------------------
CHECK FOR EVENTS
------------------------------------------------------------

for each trigger in current map triggers
  if trigger is at hero position and is armed
    fire trigger
    if trigger is auto off
      disable trigger

------------------------------------------------------------
NAVIGATE HERO
------------------------------------------------------------

move hero in given direction
increment step count

if current location is solid
  move hero back in opposite direction
else
  check for battle encounter
  if step counter in battle range
    spawn enemies
    reset step counter
  50% chance of taking hero vitality ? ...dunno what this was

------------------------------------------------------------






